examples.en: The concert will be emceed by the actor Roger Moore.

examples.en: She was still afraid to trust her voice with words. (J. Moore)
Moore escaped by the simple expedient of lying down in a clump of grass.
examples.ru: Муру помогла сбежать простая уловка: он залёг в зарослях травы.
